msgid "Specify the number of complete loops to automatically play through a set of slides. Set to <span class=\"code\">%1$s</span> or <span class=\"code\">%2$s</span> for an infinite loop. Carousel must be active with both parameters set: <a href=\"%3$s\">%4$s</a> and <a href=\"%5$s\">%6$s</a>."
msgstr "Specify the number of complete loops to automatically play through a set of slides. Set to <span class=\"code\">%1$s</span> or <span class=\"code\">%2$s</span> for an infinite loop. Carousel must be active with both parameters set: <a href=\"%3$s\">%4$s</a> and <a href=\"%5$s\">%6$s</a>."

#. translators: 1: parameter value for switching author name in review
#. listings, 2: parameter value for setting author details to appear inline in
#. the review listings, 3: list of available elements
#: templates/settings.php:1023
msgid "Change the ordering within review item: review text may be set to appear at the top of each entry. Add <em>%1$s</em> to switch the author’s avatar and name with stars and date. Add <em>%2$s</em> to set the author name, stars and date inline. Individual elements can be set and ordered using a comma separated list (e.g. <em>%3$s</em>)."
msgstr "Change the ordering within review item: review text may be set to appear at the top of each entry. Add <em>%1$s</em> to switch the author’s avatar and name with stars and date. Add <em>%2$s</em> to set the author name, stars, and date inline. Individual elements can be set and ordered using a comma-separated list (eg <em>%3$s</em>)."

#. translators: 1: parameter value for switching author name in review
#. listings, 2: parameter value for setting author details to appear inline in
#. the review listings
#: templates/settings.php:958
